Leave those thousand days and thousand nights, which exist no more<br />
You can&#8217;t know that they have ever been<br />
Take the very day you&#8217;ve hidden on the heart&#8217;s side<br />
You will never ever forget it</p>
<p>This was your day of love<br />
A most beautiful day, that never ends<br />
The world lives for a day of love<br />
A day that gives you everything and takes it away<br />
You never know that</p>
<p>When will this day come for you again<br />
Don&#8217;t let hope go away<br />
Fall asleep when the morning wakes you up<br />
This will be a day of love</p>
